87
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,640
from him and mail them to me.

88
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,240
I'm waiting for your return.

89
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,080
Heroine, what do

90
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,040
we need from Li Bugui?

91
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,720
His hair,

92
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:25,360
blood and tears.

93
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,320
Huh?

94
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,600
Isn't it so hard

95
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,000
to get those things

96
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,360
from him?

97
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,240
Yes.

98
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,480
Show yourself.

99
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,520
You've become more cautious

100
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,200
since you robbed that spiritual officer.

101
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,520
Because

102
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,039
