117
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,080
to look for Ji Bofeng.

118
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,480
Why don't you ask the girls

119
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,640
in brothels instead of me?

120
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,240
They even know

121
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,760
