126
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,440
Then won't it be more efficient

127
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,280
for you to ask them?

128
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,080
All right.

129
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,239
It seems

130
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,840
