131
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,160
Yes.

132
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,000
Could you clean up the yard for me?

133
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:06,599
Sure.

134
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,159
But...

135
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,120
But?

136
